2.0.0.name: sim/keypad
2.0.0.description: This plugin attaches a popup keyboard to a text field for mouse-driven entry or adds an inline keypad in a division or span. * Customise keypad content. * Preset keyboard layouts. * Randomise key positions. * 9 localisations.
